{"tid":1715754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突然停課有古惑","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:20:53.000Z","uid":269706,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"36bdaf59cb8781b007718d4a85f54493d5475214","tid":1715754,"uid":269706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"自知P牌<br />\n之前林鄭上電視講咩圈套個時, 條眉戚一戚,好似話俾人知佢自己好撚醒....<br />\n今日就話聽日停課....一定有古惑<br />\n<br />\n黑警究竟會唔會番兜中大?<br />\n定係跳任打港大呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根據打機既經驗, 咁既情況, 對我方最不利既, 就係要 - 估</span><br />\n估錯一次就可能無幾百手足...<br />\n<br />\n中間D分析....唔好晒時間,唔講<br />\n<br />\n要破解對家既招式, 可以用以下策略, 就係 - <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;我唔估, 我要你估!!!!!&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係....手足預告, 只要你攻任何一到, 大學/IVE/中小學, 或者XXXX<br />\n前線就會攻政總/禮賓府/立法會/和你塞/和你飛/XXX......其中一樣<br />\n(當然同時會力守)<br />\n<br />\n好處就係, <br />\n- 唔駛談判<br />\n- 壓力去左黑警+777<br />\n- 問題係由黑警+777引發<br />\n- 擺明車馬, 要停就5大訴求+解散黑警"},{"pid":"6c1253fb4b3440193a622d41f6dc75dd862aa23e","tid":1715754,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續啊繼續啊繼續啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民同我早早早早早起，繼續無限三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人已經退無可退！Neve forgive. Never forget. </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyOjWTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyOjWTe.jpg&h=fd7333c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzLMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdzLMW.jpg&h=f251c786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b67a8843e521e1451e9c30d779ce72cf0fcdede","tid":1715754,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"